platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Worlds to discover, aliens to encounter—a giant cosmos awaits in this epic strategy game from the makers of the Civilization series. To expand your federation, you’ll guide a space fleet from system to system, letting you build alliances, collect resources, and research new technology. When you’re not immersed in those rich details, you’ll be facing enemy vessels in blistering turn-based battles. The whole struggle for galactic control feels exciting and rewarding but (thanks to a helpful hint system) never too overwhelming.
